As fashion month kicks off across the pond, the style maven attended a fragrance launch last night, turning heads in a beautifully crafted mini dress. Model/presenter/author/all round IT girl Alexa was in The Big Apple to support her fashion designer friend Christian Siriano as he launched his debut fragrance. 
